Gridania.Name: Close to Home
Gridania.Description: Miounne, proprietress of the Carline Canopy, wants you to perform three tasks that will help you learn the fundamentals of adventuring.

Gridania.Name: To the Bannock
Gridania.Description: Miounne wishes to send an adventurer to the instructor at the Bannock.

Gridania.Name: Passing Muster
Gridania.Description: Galfrid, chief instructor at the Bannock, wishes to inspect your equipment and thereby gauge your readiness for future missions.

Gridania.Name: Chasing Shadows
Gridania.Description: Galfrid needs an adventurer to investigate suspicious activity in the Twelveswood.

Gridania.Name: Eggs over Queasy
Gridania.Description: Galfrid, chief instructor at the Bannock, wishes you to collect chigoe egg sacs.

Gridania.Name: Surveying the Damage
Gridania.Description: A guard at Gilbert's Spire named Monranguin needs you to recover the surveying equipment left behind in a cave by a startled recruit.

Gridania.Name: A Soldier's Breakfast
Gridania.Description: Pauline at Gabineaux's Bower needs an adventurer to cull the growing anole population, as well as gather one of the scalekin's eggs.

Gridania.Name: Spirithold Broken
Gridania.Description: Galfrid, chief instructor at the Bannock, would entrust you with the task of investigating Spirithold.

Gridania.Name: On to Bentbranch
Gridania.Description: Impressed by your progress, Miounne wishes to send you on to Bentbranch Meadows, where you will find further opportunities to learn.

Gridania.Name: You Shall Not Trespass
Gridania.Description: Keitha, the head wrangler at Bentbranch Meadows, appears most distraught. See if there is anything you can do.

Gridania.Name: Don't Look Down
Gridania.Description: Osha Jaab, a Wood Wailer at the Matron's Lethe, is looking for a sure-footed adventurer to pluck blue trumpets from the root of the nearby heavenspillar.

Gridania.Name: In the Grim Darkness of the Forest
Gridania.Description: Theodore is looking for an adventurer to deliver a message.

Gridania.Name: Threat Level Elevated
Gridania.Description: Roseline would like you to warn other sentries of the stranger's activities.

Gridania.Name: Migrant Marauders
Gridania.Description: Eylgar would like to impose upon the kindness of an adventurer.

Gridania.Name: A Hearer Is Often Late
Gridania.Description: Lothaire, a guard at Galvanth's Spire, wants you to visit the Hedgetree.

Gridania.Name: Salvaging the Scene
Gridania.Description: Armelle, a local at the Mirror Planks, wishes you to salvage cargo from a wreckage on the road.

Gridania.Name: Leia's Legacy
Gridania.Description: Luquelot at Bentbranch Meadows seeks your assistance in finding a lost chocobo egg.

Gridania.Name: Dread Is in the Air
Gridania.Description: Luquelot appears to be in need of assistance.

Gridania.Name: To Guard a Guardian
Gridania.Description: Miounne has a mind to assign you a mission of great import.

Gridania.Name: Festive Endeavors
Gridania.Description: Bowlord Lewin has information regarding your role in Greenbliss.

Gridania.Name: Renewing the Covenant
Gridania.Description: Miounne has some final words of advice to offer regarding your role in Greenbliss.

Gridania.Name: The Gridanian Envoy
Gridania.Description: Kan–E–Senna would entrust you with a task of great import.

Ul'dah.Name: Close to Home
Ul'dah.Description: Momodi, the proprietress of the Quicksand, wants you to perform three tasks that will help you learn the fundamentals of adventuring.

Ul'dah.Name: We Must Rebuild
Ul'dah.Description: Momodi of the Quicksand wants to introduce you to a certain someone at the Ul'dah Dispatch Yard.

Ul'dah.Name: Nothing to See Here
Ul'dah.Description: Stationmaster Papashan has a simple task for a fledgling adventurer.

Ul'dah.Name: Underneath the Sultantree
Ul'dah.Description: Papashan is in dire need of your assistance.

Ul'dah.Name: Step Nine
Ul'dah.Description: Cicidoa needs a reliable adventurer to deliver a gift to the Coffer & Coffin.

Ul'dah.Name: Prudence at This Junction
Ul'dah.Description: Roger hears all sorts of information in his line of work, some of which may be useful to you.

Ul'dah.Name: Out of House and Home
Ul'dah.Description: Warin has work for an adventurer willing to exterminate the coblyns attacking ore wagons.

Ul'dah.Name: Way Down in the Hole
Ul'dah.Description: Zuzumeda wishes to share with you a most amazing rumor.

Ul'dah.Name: Takin' What They're Givin'
Ul'dah.Description: Momodi of the Quicksand has word of work for a willing adventurer.

Ul'dah.Name: Supply and Demands
Ul'dah.Description: Dadanen would like you to deliver a message to Copperbell Mines.

Ul'dah.Name: Give It to Me Raw
Ul'dah.Description: Drunken Stag needs someone to retrieve the raw Nashachite he dropped outside the mines.

Ul'dah.Name: The Perfect Swarm
Ul'dah.Description: Drunken Stag wishes to repay your kindness with some useful information.

Ul'dah.Name: Last Letter to Lost Hope
Ul'dah.Description: Fufulupa wants you to track down a missing courier.

Ul'dah.Name: Heir Today, Gone Tomorrow
Ul'dah.Description: Leofric has a request for an adventurer looking to do some good.

Ul'dah.Name: Passing the Blade
Ul'dah.Description: Leofric would like you to deliver an item to Horizon.

Ul'dah.Name: Following Footfalls
Ul'dah.Description: Fufulupa needs you to assist his fellow Brass Blades.

Ul'dah.Name: Storms on the Horizon
Ul'dah.Description: Nunuzofu wants you to deliver a message to Crescent Cove.

Ul'dah.Name: Oh Captain, My Captain
Ul'dah.Description: Merilda may have stumbled upon a secret...

Ul'dah.Name: Secrets and Lies
Ul'dah.Description: Fufulupa would entrust you with a matter of grave import.

Ul'dah.Name: Duty, Honor, Country
Ul'dah.Description: Momodi wishes to enlist the aid of a trusted friend of Ul'dah.

Ul'dah.Name: A Matter of Tradition
Ul'dah.Description: Owyne would like to speak with you regarding the sultana's invitation.

Ul'dah.Name: A Royal Reception
Ul'dah.Description: Momodi wants to see you off to the banquet.

Ul'dah.Name: The Ul'dahn Envoy
Ul'dah.Description: Raubahn means to entrust you with a task of the utmost import.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Close to Home
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Baderon, proprietor of the Drowning Wench, wants you to perform three tasks that will help you learn the fundamentals of adventuring.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: On to Summerford
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Baderon, proprietor of the Drowning Wench, wants you to lend a hand at Summerford Farms.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Dressed to Call
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Staelwyrn, owner of Summerford Farms, wishes to inspect your equipment and thereby gauge your readiness for the tasks he has in mind.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Lurkers in the Grotto
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Staelwyrn, the owner of Summerford Farms, has a task for a competent adventurer.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Washed Up
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Staelwyrn is up in arms, as his hired hands are nowhere to be found.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Double Dealing
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Staelwyrn worries his sack of oranges will not reach the La Thagran Checkpoint as planned.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Loam Maintenance
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Gurcant seeks fertile soil to improve the yields of his newly plowed fields.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Plowshares to Swords
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Pfrewahl needs stolen farm tools recovered.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Just Deserts
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Staelwyrn has reason to believe that Sevrin is up to no good. Something must be done.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Sky-high
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Baderon, the proprietor of the Drowning Wench, has a suggestion to put you on the road towards new adventures.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Thanks a Million
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Wyrkrhit, a Skylift operator, needs you to recover a cargo load abandoned by a terrified wagon driver and deliver it to its intended recipient.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Relighting the Torch
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Fraeloef, a Yellowjacket on guard duty in Swiftperch, wants you to visit the Brewer's Beacon and investigate the reason behind the waning light.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: On to the Drydocks
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Forgemaster H'naanza, head of Naldiq & Vymelli's, wants you to assist with the workload over at the Moraby Drydocks.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Without a Doubt
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Ahtbyrm is looking for a member of his crew and the items he was supposed to deliver.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Righting the Shipwright
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Haldbroda has a suggestion for the kind adventurer who came bearing foreman Ahtbyrm's message.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Do Angry Pirates Dream
Limsa Lominsa.Description: <Emphasis>Victory</Emphasis> foreman Ahtbyrm is considering recommending you for an important job involving drydock security.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Victory in Peril
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Ghimthota, a captain of the watch at the Moraby Drydocks, wishes your aid in dealing with potential intruders.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Men of the Blue Tattoos
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Ghimthota wishes to entrust you with an important task.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: Feint and Strike
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Baderon has a task for a trusted adventurer.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: High Society
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Commodore Reyner wishes to speak with you regarding the forthcoming banquet.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: A Mizzenmast Repast
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Baderon wants you to let him know when you are ready to depart for the banquet.

Limsa Lominsa.Name: The Lominsan Envoy
Limsa Lominsa.Description: Merlwyb wishes to entrust you with an important task.

Main Quest Line.Name: Call of the Sea
Main Quest Line.Description: The serpent officer has information that may be of interest to you.

Main Quest Line.Name: It's Probably Pirates
Main Quest Line.Description: Baderon, the proprietor of the Drowning Wench, has need of a capable adventurer.

Main Quest Line.Name: Call of the Forest
Main Quest Line.Description: Baderon has information on a new task.

Main Quest Line.Name: Fire in the Gloom
Main Quest Line.Description: Miounne is waiting to brief you on your task.

Main Quest Line.Name: Call of the Desert
Main Quest Line.Description: Miounne has information on a new task.

Main Quest Line.Name: Into a Copper Hell
Main Quest Line.Description: Momodi is waiting to brief you on your task.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Scions of the Seventh Dawn
Main Quest Line.Description: Momodi is ready to tell you what she knows about the Scions of the Seventh Dawn.

Main Quest Line.Name: A Wild Rose by Any Other Name
Main Quest Line.Description: Minfilia is waiting to hear whether or not you will pledge your support to the Scions of the Seventh Dawn.

Main Quest Line.Name: Unsolved Mystery
Main Quest Line.Description: Isembard of Camp Drybone is seeking help to solve a mystery of missing persons.

Main Quest Line.Name: What Poor People Think
Main Quest Line.Description: Isembard aims to turn his investigation to the commonfolk.

Main Quest Line.Name: A Proper Burial
Main Quest Line.Description: Isembard would like you to learn what you can from the clergy.

Main Quest Line.Name: For the Children
Main Quest Line.Description: Isembard is concerned about the questions surrounding Sister Ourcen's integrity.

Main Quest Line.Name: Amalj'aa Wrong Places
Main Quest Line.Description: Isembard seems to have a message for you from Thancred.

Main Quest Line.Name: Dressed to Deceive
Main Quest Line.Description: Isembard wants to help you identify and apprehend the false priest.

Main Quest Line.Name: Life, Materia and Everything
Main Quest Line.Description: Minfilia would like you to meet a distinguished individual.

Main Quest Line.Name: Lord of the Inferno
Main Quest Line.Description: Minfilia would like you to assist the Immortal Flames.

Main Quest Line.Name: A Hero in the Making
Main Quest Line.Description: Minfilia is wearing a wry smile. Might it have something to do with your newfound fame?

Main Quest Line.Name: The Company You Keep (Immortal Flames)
Main Quest Line.Description: The Immortal Flames recruitment officer seems eager to welcome you to Ul'dah's Grand Company.

Main Quest Line.Name: For Coin and Country
Main Quest Line.Description: The personnel officer stands ready to complete your induction into the ranks.

Main Quest Line.Name: Sylph-management
Main Quest Line.Description: Minfilia needs you to investigate the sylphs.

Main Quest Line.Name: We Come in Peace
Main Quest Line.Description: Commander Vorsaile Heuloix has been awaiting the aid of the Scions.

Main Quest Line.Name: Sylphic Studies
Main Quest Line.Description: Rolfe Hawthorne, patriarch of the beekeeping Hawthorne family, is said to be well versed in sylphic customs.

Main Quest Line.Name: First Impressions
Main Quest Line.Description: Rolfe Hawthorne would share further knowledge to assist you in befriending the sylphs.

Main Quest Line.Name: First Contact
Main Quest Line.Description: Rolfe Hawthorne has gift wrapped your offering in preparation for your journey into the sylphs' demesne.

Main Quest Line.Name: Dance Dance Diplomacy
Main Quest Line.Description: Yda has a notion of how one might earn the sylphs' trust.

Main Quest Line.Name: Forest Friend
Main Quest Line.Description: Papalymo has a notion of how you might endear yourself to the sylphs of Little Solace.

Main Quest Line.Name: Presence of the Enemy
Main Quest Line.Description: Komuxio of Little Solace would entrust you with a task.

Main Quest Line.Name: Brotherly Love
Main Quest Line.Description: Komuxio is pining for a wayward friend.

Main Quest Line.Name: Spirited Away
Main Quest Line.Description: Komuxio would make a confession to you.

Main Quest Line.Name: Druthers House Rules
Main Quest Line.Description: Buscarron could use an adventurer to douse a fight brewing at his establishment.

Main Quest Line.Name: Never Forget
Main Quest Line.Description: The eponymous proprietor of Buscarron's Druthers has need of an able adventurer.

Main Quest Line.Name: Microbrewing
Main Quest Line.Description: Teteroon has places for you to go and thingies for you to get.

Main Quest Line.Name: Like Fine Wine
Main Quest Line.Description: Teteroon appears to have finished his gift for Buscarron.

Main Quest Line.Name: Sylphish Concerns
Main Quest Line.Description: If Buscarron had his druthers, he'd have an adventurer with whom to share talk of sylphs.

Main Quest Line.Name: Nouveau Riche
Main Quest Line.Description: Buscarron has more work for a willing adventurer.

Main Quest Line.Name: Into the Beast's Maw
Main Quest Line.Description: Buscarron has reliable information regarding the whereabouts of the sylph elder.

Main Quest Line.Name: A Simple Gift
Main Quest Line.Description: Buscarron has something he wants delivered to the sylphs.

Main Quest Line.Name: Believe in Your Sylph
Main Quest Line.Description: Komuxio wants you to discuss peace with Frixio.

Main Quest Line.Name: Back from the Wood
Main Quest Line.Description: Commander Heuloix appears to have more to say.

Main Quest Line.Name: Shadow of Darkness
Main Quest Line.Description: Minfilia would have you investigate the mysterious Lahabrea.

Main Quest Line.Name: Highbridge Times
Main Quest Line.Description: Hihibaru wants to help you find Lahabrea...maybe.

Main Quest Line.Name: Where There Is Smoke
Main Quest Line.Description: Hihibaru has information that will <Emphasis>surely</Emphasis> lead you to Lahabrea.

Main Quest Line.Name: On to Little Ala Mhigo
Main Quest Line.Description: Hihibaru has a suggestion to help you with your investigation.

Main Quest Line.Name: Tea for Three
Main Quest Line.Description: Gisilbehrt would like to aid in your manhunt.

Main Quest Line.Name: Foot in the Door
Main Quest Line.Description: Gisilbehrt would offer you some advice regarding your investigation.

Main Quest Line.Name: Meeting with the Resistance
Main Quest Line.Description: Minfilia wants to introduce you to an Ala Mhigan member of the Scions.

Main Quest Line.Name: Killing Him Softly
Main Quest Line.Description: Meffrid needs help tending a wounded brother.

Main Quest Line.Name: Helping Horn
Main Quest Line.Description: Meffrid needs your help to save a wounded comrade.

Main Quest Line.Name: He Ain't Heavy
Main Quest Line.Description: Meffrid needs your help to find a missing comrade.

Main Quest Line.Name: Come Highly Recommended
Main Quest Line.Description: Meffrid wishes to repay your kindness.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Bear and the Young'uns' Cares
Main Quest Line.Description: Gundobald is willing to share with you what he knows of the masked stranger.

Main Quest Line.Name: Wilred Wants You
Main Quest Line.Description: Hremfing has a secret message for you.

Main Quest Line.Name: Big Trouble in Little Ala Mhigo
Main Quest Line.Description: Gundobald needs your help to rein in the young ones of Little Ala Mhigo.

Main Quest Line.Name: Back to Square One
Main Quest Line.Description: Gundobald wants to wish you well on your investigation.

Main Quest Line.Name: Terror at Fallgourd
Main Quest Line.Description: Minfilia has another lead for you to pursue.

Main Quest Line.Name: Ziz Is So Ridiculous
Main Quest Line.Description: Aideen has a proposal to make concerning your investigation.

Main Quest Line.Name: Rock of Rancor
Main Quest Line.Description: Aideen has further knowledge of the mysterious deaths.

Main Quest Line.Name: Power of Deduction
Main Quest Line.Description: Medrod is troubled by the dearth of new developments in the murder investigation.

Main Quest Line.Name: Secret of the White Lily
Main Quest Line.Description: Aethelmaer wants you to hold on to the button.

Main Quest Line.Name: Skeletons in Her Closet
Main Quest Line.Description: Ursandel has a confession to make regarding the mysterious murders.

Main Quest Line.Name: Wrath of the Titan
Main Quest Line.Description: Minfilia is waiting to brief you and your fellow Scions on a new development.

Main Quest Line.Name: Tales from the Tidus Slayer
Main Quest Line.Description: Trachtoum is eager to regale you with stories of his glory days.

Main Quest Line.Name: Hungry Hungry Goobbues
Main Quest Line.Description: Trachtoum appears to be ignoring you.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Lominsan Way
Main Quest Line.Description: Trachtoum remains unconvinced of your readiness to defeat the dread primal Tidus.

Main Quest Line.Name: Nix That
Main Quest Line.Description: Wheiskaet would first like to verify that you are not a complete fraud.

Main Quest Line.Name: A Modest Proposal
Main Quest Line.Description: Wheiskaet has an important mission for you.

Main Quest Line.Name: Trial by Turtle
Main Quest Line.Description: Landenel needs to explain a few things to you.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Perfect Prey
Main Quest Line.Description: U'odh Nunh wants you to hunt the most dangerous game.

Main Quest Line.Name: When the Worm Turns
Main Quest Line.Description: U'odh Nunh is finally willing to tell you of the ingredient you seek.

Main Quest Line.Name: There and Back Again
Main Quest Line.Description: U'odh Nunh would like you to deliver a gift to Wheiskaet.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Things We Do for Cheese
Main Quest Line.Description: Wheiskaet would like to tell you about the final ingredient needed for the banquet.

Main Quest Line.Name: What Do You Mean You Forgot the Wine
Main Quest Line.Description: Wheiskaet would like to congratulate you on a job well done.

Main Quest Line.Name: An Offer You Can Refuse
Main Quest Line.Description: Shamani Lohmani would like to discuss wine with you.

Main Quest Line.Name: It Won't Work
Main Quest Line.Description: Shamani Lohmani has another bright idea.

Main Quest Line.Name: Give a Man a Drink
Main Quest Line.Description: Shamani Lohmani appears to be in deep thought.

Main Quest Line.Name: That Weight
Main Quest Line.Description: Drest is suffering from extreme duress.

Main Quest Line.Name: Battle Scars
Main Quest Line.Description: Drest appears to be in greater control of his faculties.

Main Quest Line.Name: It Was a Very Good Year
Main Quest Line.Description: Shamani Lohmani is brimming with glee, and he wishes to share the reason why with you.

Main Quest Line.Name: In the Company of Heroes
Main Quest Line.Description: Y'shtola is concerned for your well-being.

Main Quest Line.Name: As You Wish
Main Quest Line.Description: Wheiskaet truly intends to tell you how you may face Titan this time.

Main Quest Line.Name: Lord of Crags
Main Quest Line.Description: Riol is waiting for you to give him your undivided attention.

Main Quest Line.Name: All Good Things
Main Quest Line.Description: Y'shtola is keen to discuss your next task.

Main Quest Line.Name: You Can't Take It with You
Main Quest Line.Description: Marques has a personal request to make of you.

Main Quest Line.Name: Bringing out the Dead
Main Quest Line.Description: Sister Eluned is staring at you with great sadness in her eyes...

Main Quest Line.Name: Bury Me Not on the Lone Prairie
Main Quest Line.Description: Sister Eluned wishes to discuss one of the Scions who perished at the Waking Sands.

Main Quest Line.Name: Eyes on Me
Main Quest Line.Description: Marques believes he is being watched.

Main Quest Line.Name: He Who Waited Behind
Main Quest Line.Description: Father Iliud has some parting words for you and the others.

Main Quest Line.Name: Cold Reception
Main Quest Line.Description: Vortefaurt wishes to tell you of the final flight of the <Emphasis>Enterprise</Emphasis>.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Unending War
Main Quest Line.Description: Ser Ludovoix is doing his utmost to intimidate you into leaving.

Main Quest Line.Name: Men of Honor
Main Quest Line.Description: Jocea is attempting to attract your attention.

Main Quest Line.Name: Three for Three
Main Quest Line.Description: Lord Portelaine requires that you perform a third task on behalf of House Durendaire.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Rose and the Unicorn
Main Quest Line.Description: Ser Carrilaut has something very important to tell you.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Talk of Coerthas
Main Quest Line.Description: Lord Haurchefant has a proposal for how you might participate in his investigation.

Main Quest Line.Name: Road to Redemption
Main Quest Line.Description: Lord Haurchefant is concerned for Lord Francel's well-being.

Main Quest Line.Name: Following the Evidence
Main Quest Line.Description: Lord Haurchefant suspects that someone is conspiring against Lord Francel.

Main Quest Line.Name: In the Eyes of Gods and Men
Main Quest Line.Description: Lord Haurchefant needs your help to clear Lord Francel's name.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Final Flight of the Enterprise
Main Quest Line.Description: Lord Haurchefant would like to introduce you to his witness.

Main Quest Line.Name: Ye of Little Faith
Main Quest Line.Description: Ser Brunadier seems ill inclined to help you...

Main Quest Line.Name: Factual Folklore
Main Quest Line.Description: Haustefort is eyeing you with interest.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Best Inventions
Main Quest Line.Description: Cid would like to furnish the infirmary with a new alembic.

Main Quest Line.Name: Influencing Inquisitors
Main Quest Line.Description: Cid is concerned about Inquisitor Guillaime.

Main Quest Line.Name: By the Lights of Ishgard
Main Quest Line.Description: Alphinaud appears to be in deep thought.

Main Quest Line.Name: Blood for Blood
Main Quest Line.Description: Alphinaud is determined to discover Inquisitor Guillaime's true identity.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Heretic among Us
Main Quest Line.Description: Lord Drillemont requires your assistance in bringing the heretic masquerading as Inquisitor Guillaime to justice.

Main Quest Line.Name: In Pursuit of the Past
Main Quest Line.Description: Alphinaud is eager to enter the Stone Vigil.

Main Quest Line.Name: Into the Eye of the Storm
Main Quest Line.Description: Cid appears to be deep in thought.

Main Quest Line.Name: Sealed with Science
Main Quest Line.Description: Professor Lamberteint is about to show you something you will never forget.

Main Quest Line.Name: With the Utmost Care
Main Quest Line.Description: Hahasako is trying very hard to contain his excitement and is failing.

Main Quest Line.Name: A Promising Prospect
Main Quest Line.Description: Professor Lamberteint knows where you might find the crystal you seek.

Main Quest Line.Name: It's Probably Not Pirates
Main Quest Line.Description: Ceana is frustrated with the progress of her research.

Main Quest Line.Name: Representing the Representative
Main Quest Line.Description: Ceana seems to have regained her composure.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Reluctant Researcher
Main Quest Line.Description: Ceana has no desire to journey to the Isles of Umbra.

Main Quest Line.Name: Sweet Somethings
Main Quest Line.Description: Davyd has a simple proposal for you.

Main Quest Line.Name: History Repeating
Main Quest Line.Description: Davyd is sweating profusely...

Main Quest Line.Name: The Curious Case of Giggity
Main Quest Line.Description: Ceana knows where the corrupted crystal that you seek can be found.

Main Quest Line.Name: Better Late than Never
Main Quest Line.Description: Hedyn has neglected to return to you your corrupted crystal.

Main Quest Line.Name: Lady of the Vortex
Main Quest Line.Description: With Cid's modifications now installed, the <Emphasis>Enterprise</Emphasis> is finally ready to make the journey to the Howling Eye.

Main Quest Line.Name: Reclamation
Main Quest Line.Description: Alphinaud is ready to return to the Waking Sands.

Main Quest Line.Name: Casing the Castrum
Main Quest Line.Description: Y'shtola wishes to discuss the fate of the prisoners being held at Castrum Centri.

Main Quest Line.Name: Eyes on the Empire
Main Quest Line.Description: Lord Portelaine would like to aid in your search for Biggs and Wedge.

Main Quest Line.Name: Footprints in the Snow
Main Quest Line.Description: Ser Pierremons wants to share with you what he knows of the two fugitives.

Main Quest Line.Name: Monumental Hopes
Main Quest Line.Description: Wedge is gravely concerned for his missing companion.

Main Quest Line.Name: Notorious Biggs
Main Quest Line.Description: Wedge is determined to find Biggs.

Main Quest Line.Name: Come-Into-My-Castrum
Main Quest Line.Description: Cid wants to prepare a strategy to rescue Minfilia and the other Scions.

Main Quest Line.Name: Getting Even with Garlemald
Main Quest Line.Description: Glaumunt would like to aid in your mission to rescue the captured Scions.

Main Quest Line.Name: Acting the Part
Main Quest Line.Description: Glaumunt wants you to practice the part of imperial trooper.

Main Quest Line.Name: Dressed for Conquest
Main Quest Line.Description: Sark Malark wishes to help you acquire the disguises you need for your rescue mission.

Main Quest Line.Name: Fool Me Twice
Main Quest Line.Description: Glaumunt has finally devised a plan to appropriate a suit of magitek armor.

Main Quest Line.Name: Every Little Thing She Does Is Magitek
Main Quest Line.Description: Cid would have you assist in the repair of the magitek armor.

Main Quest Line.Name: Escape from Castrum Centri
Main Quest Line.Description: Cid awaits confirmation of your readiness to undertake the rescue mission.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Black Wolf's Ultimatum
Main Quest Line.Description: Minfilia is greatly concerned by recent developments concerning the council of the Alliance leaders.

Main Quest Line.Name: Operation Archon
Main Quest Line.Description: Minfilia would brief you on the Eorzean Alliance's planned counteroffensive against the Empire.

Main Quest Line.Name: A Hero in Need
Main Quest Line.Description: The Allied communications officer has a task that can only be performed by a hero of the Alliance.

Main Quest Line.Name: Hearts on Fire
Main Quest Line.Description: Sergeant Cracked Fist needs a hero to raise morale on the front lines.

Main Quest Line.Name: Rock the Castrum
Main Quest Line.Description: Edelstein would send you forth to commence the penultimate phase of Operation Archon.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Ultimate Weapon
Main Quest Line.Description: Raubahn has some parting words for you ahead of the final phase of Operation Archon.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Price of Principles
Main Quest Line.Description: Minfilia appears to be lost in thought.

Main Quest Line.Name: Moving On
Main Quest Line.Description: Once again, Minfilia appears to be lost in thought.

Main Quest Line.Name: All Things in Time
Main Quest Line.Description: F'lhaminn has made her peace and is ready to reunite with her adopted daughter.

Main Quest Line.Name: Laying the Foundation
Main Quest Line.Description: Minfilia would share with you the latest news on the Scions' imminent relocation.

Main Quest Line.Name: It's Possibly a Primal
Main Quest Line.Description: Slafborn would show you around the Scions' soon-to-be home in Revenant's Toll.

Main Quest Line.Name: Hail to the King, Kupo
Main Quest Line.Description: Vorsaile Heuloix wishes to brief you on the latest crisis in Gridania.

Main Quest Line.Name: You Have Selected Regicide
Main Quest Line.Description: Brother E–Sumi–Yan would unfold to you the secrets of Good King Moggle Mog XII's magical defenses.

Main Quest Line.Name: On the Properties of Primals
Main Quest Line.Description: Raya–O–Senna wishes to congratulate you on your victory over Good King Moggle Mog XII.

Main Quest Line.Name: The Gifted
